    <content type="html"><![CDATA[
      

  
  

  
    

    
      
        
        

        
          <h3>What’s New</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Account setup is updated to support OAuth2 granular permissions</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        
          </ul>
        

        
          <h3>Fixed</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird could crash when using return receipt with OWL add-on</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Folder pane display was blank due to invalid mail server hostname</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Some users were unable to log in to Microsoft 365</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Matrix end-to-end encryption tab in account settings could be shown for XMPP account</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Participant and message were not populated when user left the room using XMPP</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Visual and UX improvements</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
    </ul>
  
  

<p>As always, you’re encouraged to <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/questions/new/thunderbird">tell us what you think</a>, or <a href="https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/">file a bug in Bugzilla</a></p>
