          <p>Quick Filter reset sort type in threaded views sorted by "Order Received" ascending</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Display names for SMTP servers could be incorrectly formatted as a date</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Importing profiles from SeaMonkey did not work in certain circumstances</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Calendar events filter no longer allowed searching past or all events</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Calendar updates were not added to cache when Thunderbird was offline</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Visual and UX improvements</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
